# Knowledge graph — generated locally by graphify hooks on every commit
# and branch switch. Tracking these 92+ files produced 12MB of diff per
# commit and unavoidable merge conflicts on graph.json / GRAPH_REPORT.md
# across branches. Regenerate with `graphify update .` on fresh clones.
